 />\n所有失敗者都只想不勞而獲"},{"pid":"11bd0318a7635da0fe8be90b5256e4decdc4ed6f","tid":495735,"uid":54371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:25:10.000Z","msg":"老母係女人<br />\n<br />\n呢啲理論post去fb俾班人tag下人like下算啦<br />\npost係連登冇用"},{"pid":"87dbb12b96774a07f461a496f1aee93a5b93e3a3","tid":495735,"uid":51585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:28:27.000Z","msg":"係香港 <br />\n有好多野 就算你堅持一世人去追求<br />\n都唔代表你可以做到"},{"pid":"0f39efbf47d9148e8ea7e3290b228b64e3d61822","tid":495735,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:52:54.000Z","msg":"樓主假膠<br />\n唔係咁多人唔識起底下話"},{"pid":"c376d2912cf91957d60b347dacda1d8742fde25b","tid":495735,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:55:03.000Z","msg":"一開始講得幾好，未睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78cfff1d16d71e7d71c7e1d1a1a0fbb80771f48f","tid":495735,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e908674dbce6a5696c91f574457c5868a53b9aa4","tid":495735,"uid":11699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:08:01.000Z","msg":"天真到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}